reviewText: I expected a treatise on rose care using the usual procedures, especially for different climates.  This simply was this man's recipes for fertilizing, spraying, and planting roses using home products.
I do like it a lot. he gives a very good advice to do it. I will full his advice and I have a feeling that is going to work.

This is a great video for all year rose care.  What I really like the most about this video and Jerry Baker is his exclusive formulas he creates on this video.  And they really work!  He uses everyday household products in his formulas.  If you love roses, this is the video for you.
